snippet: Thompson made a birdie after a fortunate ricochet to finish off a three-under-par 68 on Saturday and take a share of the third-round lead.
abstract: Lexi Thompson and Inbee Park share third-round lead in North Texas Shootout golf event; other golf news noted.
